For the rest he might have been the member of a herd , not of a so ciety . 
Self preservation was his only concern . 
Not selfishness , but mere self preservation . 
I don't mean to say that living naked in a cavern would have satis fied him . 
Obviously he was the creature of the conditions to which he was born . 
No doubt self preservation meant also the preservation of these conditions . 
