He told me this in his low , careless voice , to such a pitch of confidence had we arrived at the end of half an hour . 
It took me just about that time to convince him that I had never dreamed of marrying Hermann's niece . 
Any man with eyes in his head , he seemed to think , could not help coveting so much bodily magnifi cence . 
